      "text_excerpt": "This catalog of security and privacy controls provides protective measures for systems, organizations, and individuals.32 The controls are designed to facilitate risk management and compliance with applicable federal laws, executive orders, directives, regulations, policies, and standards. With few exceptions, the security and privacy controls in the catalog are policy-, technology-, and sector-neutral, meaning that the controls focus on the fundamental measures necessary to protect information "
